page.title: 06HEALTH
page.content: Jim Raeburn is the head of the fire department in TRANENT. He has worked there for 27yrs.He is a part time fire man.There are ten men who train weekly Dr Kennedy has worked in Tranent for 34yrs.At the Health Centre there are 9 doctors 2 are part time,3 health visitors,3 nurses and one charge nurse to cope with 12000 patients. P.C.Grant is the community policeman and has worked here for 7yrs.There are 13 policemen and 1 policewoman.Mr Boyd is one of three dentists in TRANENT He has been here for nearly four years and has 6000 patients.There is one vet and one optician. St Josephs list D school has 33 boys living in and 9 day boys. Fa'side Lodge old folks home has 26 female and 14 male residents whose average age is 82 years.There is a staff of twelve to look after them.
